and for the @samp{Approved} column@comma{} by providing an @samp{[X]} status if all
children have been checked.  The @samp{CLOCKSUM} and @samp{CLOCKSUM_T} columns
are special@comma{} they list the sums of CLOCK intervals in the subtree@comma{}
either for all clocks or just for today.

